    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and looks totally pristine inside and out. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it because I really love driving it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this dream ride. You won't find another one this clean\u2014come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
